{"type": "article", "id": 55326, "title": "红酒专用的“安全套”，继塞子之后的新主意｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-17T23:10:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 51911, "name": "Grupa Studio"}, {"id": 51912, "name": "Lepow"}, {"id": 10632, "name": "UNDERCOVER"}, {"id": 51913, "name": "EASTPAK"}, {"id": 51914, "name": "Max Hampton-Fischer"}, {"id": 51915, "name": "Tianyi Shi"}, {"id": 51916, "name": "Laura Bartlett"}, {"id": 27456, "name": "Chengtao Yi"}, {"id": 27455, "name": "Bryan Wong"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 132, "image": "img/article/article_show/201807180710377mWVua6OCNhB2v4o.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>FeC Steel Chopsticks by Chengtao Yi and Bryan Wong </h3><p>当谈论到餐具设计时，筷子被认为是最简单的。它形式简洁，表面光滑，似乎难以在造型上有重大突破，只有通过材质和装饰性元素才能区别出来。</p><p>最近，设计师 Chengtao Yi 和 Bryan Wong 在不影响筷子核心功能的基础上，设计出一款名为 FeC 不锈钢筷子，从细节处下功夫，意在赋予用户更好的使用体验。</p><p>他们希望 FeC 是可以每天陪伴用户进食的餐具，无论是在家中还是外出就餐，此外，也能减少一次性木筷的使用频率。为此，设计师还专门设计了匹配筷子大小的筷套，方便携带的同时，外观看起来更是有几分酷劲。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201543vspnWtmE7wSb9YDd.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666800\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201543g9yxeJVbrsHPEFu5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201544kFMKXVvYNWlq4CLT.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.545600\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201544LsiqB7MjlKHFR8up.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201544VGfH8JbAXWsvgj3p.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807172015445yatbFAmLicoCUPf.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647200\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807172015463LkyegRhTjoGwX61.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666800\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.chengtaoyi.com/#/fec/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chengtao Yi</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Wine Condoms by Laura Bartlett</h3><p>几年前的一个晚上，Laura Bartlett 把朋友聚会后没喝完的红酒带回家，为了保存已开封的红酒，她在瓶口套上保鲜膜和橡皮筋，儿子 Strahan 看到后，开玩笑说，像是个“安全套”。正是这个玩笑，给了母子俩灵感，他们决定做一款红酒专用的“安全套”，开始设计产品、logo 以及包装。</p><p>Wine Condoms 的原材料是橡胶，弹性与长度根据红酒瓶设计，套上后就算把酒瓶倒转，酒也不会漏出来。一套 6 个售价 15 美元，<a href=\"https://winecondoms.com/products/box-of-wine-condoms\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201632zoHr9YfLXDmsOxCt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201632EV7CY4Ipj8ZPmxqe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201632Ce5x8wHmorME9u3j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201632NLVKvdA8Szpj7eIB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201633BEt9W1frSwyR3CGj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523560\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://winecondoms.com/products/box-of-wine-condoms\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wine Condoms</a></p></figcaption></figure></div><h3>EASTPAK BY UNDERCOVER</h3><p>美国箱包品牌 EASTPAK，最近与日本时尚品牌 UNDERCOVER 合作，发布联名系列背包，其中最具代表性的产品，是 EASTPAK 的Padded Pak’r® 背包的更新款，采用 100% 聚酰胺纤维于日本制作，以黑、红、绿三色呈现。</p><p>整个背包最点睛的部分，在于库布里克经典科幻杰作《2001：太空漫游》的字句，点缀于包身之上，而“Logic Memory Center”字样，更是对 HAL 9000 致敬。售价 257 美元，<a href=\"https://www.luisaviaroma.com/en-us/p/eastpak-by-undercover/women/backpacks/68I-WMZ001?ColorId=NzBX0&amp;SubLine=bags&amp;CategoryId=82&amp;lvrid=_p_dWMZ_gw_c82\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试预购</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807172017155kP8DjFEilKBT30a.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201715j5aVfy06Msuq7iNP.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807172017163mCFzel7LAwsEx4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.luisaviaroma.com/en-us/p/eastpak-by-undercover/women/backpacks/68I-WMZ001?ColorId=NzBX0&amp;SubLine=bags&amp;CategoryId=82&amp;lvrid=_p_dWMZ_gw_c82\" rel=\"nofollow\">luisaviaroma</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Memomate by Lepow</h3><p>Memomate 是香港数码创意配件品牌 Lepow 推出的一款多功能产品，它既是智能手写板、绘图板，也可以用作手账本，当然它还是一款容量为 10000 毫安的移动电源。</p><p>尽管智能手机和电脑替代了我们绝大多数的办公、学习需求，但是仍有不少人习惯于用笔来书写、绘画。Memomate 适用于这类人群在灵感迸发的时刻使用。</p><p>它是一张可以重复书写的电子纸，既可以随心所欲涂鸦，也可以关键时刻随记随写，或是生活备忘录，轻按清除键，就可以将整个画面清除再次使用。售价 499 元，<a href=\"https://detail.youzan.com/show/goods?alias=278vcxw9a3yj7&amp;activity=\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807172018075Mskw97pxb8N6cBY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201807hUOWD5iejLXs7tkT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201807Ad5XENviZ3hnbcLx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201807h7rmwyTPecYzNLFD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201808W57LACxtTpByMg3i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.945714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201808TRWa5N4FfCb0xheY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201809ekShqEPnKJ3R2w8F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.963810\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://lepow.hk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lepow</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Möbel Chair by Tianyi Shi and Max Hampton-Fischer</h3><p>便携性、可移动成为时下不少设计师考虑产品设计时的关键词。比如这款 Möbel 椅，可以随身携带，因为它可以轻松折叠起来，便于用户移动或是搬家。</p><p>Möbel 椅出自设计师 Tianyi Shi 和 Max Hampton-Fischer 之手。它很轻，不足 9 公斤，由多层再生工业毛毡制成，这些毛毡固定在一起，在展开时形成蜂窝状图案。厚厚的毛毡层保证其坚固耐用，满足一至两个人使用。椅子内有一个金属按扣，用于折叠椅子时使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201846h3oy0WOmqLSjs7Hc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201846IbcUdDCyG60gKMm5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201846U9wvo4GT7MdybDpI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201846dHCnI45Xc1YK0Ats.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201846aOIRtydG0kCvjZpe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201847e5FjZOPDE3KIkolH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018071720184826udmqkLj7KhsPZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.957031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://stytianyi.com/mbel/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tianyi Shi</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Baluna Lamp Collection by Grupa Studio</h3><p>萨格勒布设计品牌 Grupa Studio 推出 Baluna 灯具系列，是一系列有着细微差别的几何组合灯具，设计师在构想时，考虑到了光与空间时如何相互作用的，这也成为整个系列设计的起点。</p><p>Baluna 系列由磨砂玻璃球、半圆杯钢质元件和较长的钢架和灯臂组件构成，包括不同高度的台灯、落地灯和壁灯，可以覆盖任何空间。通过不同种球体的组合，可以控制灯的方向，调光功能更是为用户提供了多样性的选择。售价 340 欧元起，<a href=\"http://www.grupaproducts.com/baluna/order/ba-tw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201933QjEKkt6qdrzumR0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201933q6o3gS9LK7ZHPwMy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201933VyNqC4poDPGha7Zl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807172019333LnHyVD7tARrQhPB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807172019359XqYgE3nRpAxJCwZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201935vkpi1Bmr9oUj2Wcs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717201935uZ6QcjBx4zUrLWhd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.grupaproducts.com/baluna/order/ba-tw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Grupa Studio</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}